Ferramentas de monitoramento:

> Instalar Psensor: $ sudo apt install psensor

> instalar smartctl: $ sudo apt install smartmontools

> Instalar ls_sensors: $ sudo apt install lm-sensors
	>> Comandos uteis: $ sudo sensors-detect  $ sensors
	
> Instalar nvme-cli: $ sudo apt install nvme-cli
	>> Comando util: $ sudo nvme smart-log /dev/nvme0n1


